00:00:22.930 --> 00:00:27.910
So let me recap the
important lecture

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:31.650
from last time that gave
the framework that we'll

00:00:31.650 --> 00:00:33.480
see in Chapter two
and Chapter three,

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.640
