00:21:01.740 --> 00:21:05.300
I'll use b's for the sines.

00:21:05.300 --> 00:21:08.610
(omega_1*t), x_1.

00:21:08.610 --> 00:21:10.670
So that's just like that.

00:21:10.670 --> 00:21:15.240
But it's used the sines, which
