00:45:23.560 --> 00:45:26.620
start with Euler, forward Euler.

00:45:26.620 --> 00:45:28.730
What'll happen?

00:45:28.730 --> 00:45:30.010
It'll spiral out.

00:45:30.010 --> 00:45:30.720
Exactly.

